channel.description:
Ok, This took me a bit, but I love helping people now :P
It is a list of all the current answered questions. I hope it helps people who are wanting to start a server!
[url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10306.0.html]How Do I Set Up NPC Hp?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10323.0.html]How Do I Enter A Server With Other People In It?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,8335.0.html]How Do I Make Myself Admin?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10338.0.html]How Do I Get To The MoparScape Log In Screen?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10311.0.html]How Do I Add Store Prices And Monster Drops?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10200.0.html]I have this error “Exception is thread “main“ java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: client“ HELP?![/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,7789.0.html]How Do I Spawn NPCs?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,8093.0.html]I Have No Idea What The Item Codes Are! Help?![/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10094.0.html]I Keep Getting A Connection Error! What Do I Do?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10150.0.html]How Do I Play On Someone Elses Server?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10135.0.html]How Do I Get The Default Server Off On To Mine?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.comsmf/index.php/topic,10019.0.html]I get this error: "'java' is not recognized as an internal or external command" or "'javac' is not recognized as an internal or external command" Help?![/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10139.0.html]How Do I Make Others Admin?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10098.0.html]HELP! When I Kill A Monster It Freezes![/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10104.0.html]I Want To Get Rid Of The “TestScape“ Scroll..How?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10049.0.html]I Can‘t Find My Client.Java[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10025.0.html]I Have This Error: Error# 25192 Error:file not found[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10058.0.html]How Do I Make My ADMIN Levels 99?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,10015.0.html]I Have This Error: " 'java' is not recognized as an internal or external command, operable program or batch file.” What Do I Do?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,9883.0.html]When I CLOSE The Client It Doesn‘t Save![/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php]Where Can I Find Other Servers Ips?[/url]
[url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=search]My Problem Isn't In There! How Do I get The Answer?[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,8716.0.html]Click Here For More Help[/url] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,6219.0.html]And Here For More Help![/url]
That is most of the answered questions. The reason there is 23 pages is because they are asked over and over again :P
I’ll update when I can with new questions.
